{"tid":1024283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺”un “腳先係真男人","createTime":"2019-02-16T12:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T11:56:13.000Z","uid":134548,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3e748cdeb35ec9e5ecc4d0e2b8aa2d3e3246ad","tid":1024283,"uid":134548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"成班老友食飯齊齊un <br />\n食飯&rdquo;烚烚&rdquo;聲 盡情表現哂男人個種真性情<br />\n不過有時見朋友帶埋條女黎 又唔比佢un腳又話食野要合埋口咀嚼 話粗魯無家教喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到之後大家食飯都變到好拘謹...<br />\n有次我用講笑既語氣講：un腳先係真男人！ 結果之後大家食飯都好少再見到我個位朋友<br />\n小弟之前都有個咁既女朋友 結果當然係飛撚左啦<br />\n唔知有無真男人巴打明..."},{"pid":"7a502c4f64d707fdf21a04cd837c2807a4874757","tid":1024283,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"巴打識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c67a06eb31e72ed8b13326ff19d2707a0f6458","tid":1024283,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"有有除埋鞋棟腳捽腳趾"},{"pid":"cf20fb080fd8d47fb84fd5b65f225780dd71fa75","tid":1024283,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56c67a06eb31e72ed8b13326ff19d2707a0f6458","tid":1024283,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"有有除埋鞋棟腳捽腳趾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"有冇"},{"pid":"de1fbb0df9ab65402cad20d4d21b1939884e9810","tid":1024283,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"我同D好熟既女仔食飯都照UN腳, 有次講開佢地話只要唔整到張枱,就冇所謂"}]}